thumb.title: Pimentel Landscaping LLC
thumb.description: Transform your outdoor space with Pimentel Landscaping, a trusted expert in landscape design, installation, and maintenance for homeowners in Mesa, Gilbert, Chandler, Queen Creek, Tempe, and Scottsdale. Along with custom design work, we specialize in bringing dream outdoor spaces to life with high-quality xeriscape conversions, hardscape and paver installations, artificial turf installations, irrigation installations, lighting installations, and plant and rock installations. When you hire our East Valley landscaping team, you can expect clear communication, expert attention to detail, and a stress-free experience from start to finish. Contact us today for a free quote on your landscaping project. Financing is available for projects from $1k-$25k.Pimentel Landscaping LLC2844 East Coralbell Avenue, Mesa, Arizona 85204+1 480-600-6343https://www.pimentellandscaping.com/
